This media type may require encoding on transports not capable of handling binary.

Security considerations :
The media type does not contain active content or other code intended to be
executed in the host environment. The media type MAY contain code intended to
run in a sandboxed emulation environment. Implementations that execute such
content MUST ensure that untrusted content is not executed in an unprotected
environment. The security considerations for this type have not been completely
assessed.
